name: Robert Marcus
description: Am Robert by name,am from New Jersey,am 50 yrs old and i have son that lives with me am a very Honest,loving,caring and easy going man who love to cherish his women i hate liers for that reason i don’t tell lies,I’ve been single for the past 6yrs but i’m damn tired of been lonely living a single life….i wanna love and be loved again……
